42:22.544 --> 42:25.422
Ready! Set! Hut-hut!

42:29.551 --> 42:34.264
- Hold them! Come on!
Yeah! Yeah! All right!

42:35.682 --> 42:37.101
Fight, damn it, fight!

42:37.976 --> 42:42.689
Fourth and goal for the Knights
on the one-yard line! This is it!

42:48.028 --> 42:54.284
Ready! Set!
- Hold them! You fucking bastards!

43:04.128 --> 43:07.548
