yard line with 12 seconds left.

43:21.270 --> 43:23.480
- We did it, Riley!
Did we do it?

43:23.647 --> 43:25.107
You did it!

43:26.483 --> 43:27.860
Rifleman!

43:28.068 --> 43:30.612
- Coach!
- I strong right, 42 condition.

43:30.779 --> 43:32.406
All right!

43:52.301 --> 43:56.513
Salvucci fumbles in
the end zone and the Knights recover.

43:56.680 --> 44:02.269
It's a touchdown! No time left. Knights
win! Touchdown. The Knights win!

45:30.148 --> 45:35.028
Come on, Salvucci.
Let's hear a good cry, all right.

45:35.195 --> 45:40.367
