hear a cry! I want to hear a good one.

45:41.034 --> 45:46.915
You choked! You cost us the game.
You quit on me and on this team.

45:47.416 --> 45:49.876
He didn't quit.

45:52.045 --> 45:54.089
What did you say?

45:57.217 --> 46:02.013
Well, Salvucci, he didn't quit.
None of us quit.

46:03.849 --> 46:08.770
I don't know. We beat those guys'
asses up and down that field tonight!

46:10.397 --> 46:15.110
