Isn't that right?

46:15.318 --> 46:20.740
You know, maybe the scoreboard
doesn't say it, but we won that game.

46:23.952 --> 46:25.829
We held them.

46:27.330 --> 46:32.085
It was just a fluke.
That's all, it's just a fluke.

46:32.252 --> 46:34.087
A fluke?

46:35.005 --> 46:39.301
That pass interference penalty,
that was no fluke.

46:39.968 --> 46:42.971
If you had done it the way
I taught you...

46:43.138 --> 46:47.893
