You're through. You're off the team.

47:48.536 --> 47:52.540
I'll see you, I gotta get on the bus.
All right.

47:52.874 --> 47:56.378
- Yeah, that's him. Right there.
Wait up.

47:59.422 --> 48:02.676
Wait a minute, wait a minute.
Where you going?

48:02.884 --> 48:05.553
