got a chance. I'm 17 years old.

56:29.556 --> 56:32.184
It's not fucking fair.

56:32.643 --> 56:37.648
And, you, you're so selfish,
you don't even see it.

56:42.403 --> 56:47.324
- God, I've been such an asshole, huh?
- Yes.

56:48.784 --> 56:50.244
Yeah.

56:52.079 --> 56:54.665
I can spell my own name, though.

56:55.916 --> 56:59.878
No, Lis, I mean, I don't know what-

57:03.090 --> 57:08.178
I'm really sorry.
