57:56.560 --> 58:00.606
You're so gorgeous,
I just can't help it. That's why.

58:02.232 --> 58:08.447
I love you so much, Lisa.
I'm sorry. I just mess up.

58:13.327 --> 58:15.788
Now I get to carry this, huh?

58:16.371 --> 58:18.165
Come on!

58:19.082 --> 58:24.963
I don't need to graduate, I need a job.
My uncle and brother are out of work.

58:25.172 --> 58:29.384
You quit school, you'll be on the
streets. How will that help?

58:29.593 --> 58:33.263
Let me make some calls.
Before you make a decision.

58:33.430 --> 58:35.599
Hey, Nick, how's it going?

58:35.766 --> 58:38.352
Sherm, how are you?
- Nice to see you.

58:38.519 --> 58:40.687
Vinnie,
Sherm Williams, Boston College.

58:40.854 --> 58:44.483
I've heard good things.
Everything okay?

58:44.650 --> 58:47.319
- That time of year again?
- Playing Pitt.

58:47.486 --> 58:49.530
- I understand, you-
- Hold it.

58:49.696 --> 58:53.367
- Vinnie. I know you're no quitter.
- What?

58:53.575 --> 58:57.287
- Don't quit on me, man.
- Right, coach.

58:57.454 --> 59:00.082
Hey, nice to meet you.

59:00.249 --> 59:04.628
I understand you had a hell
of a defense against Walnut Heights.

59:04.795 --> 59:08.298
I want to see film on Riley,
Djordjevic and Oliver.

59:08.465 --> 59:12.928
Riley and Oliver, they're good.
Djordjevic, I got to pass on.

59:13.095 --> 59:16.765
- Why? That kid's tough.
