59:35.742 --> 59:38.161
I don't know. How you doing?

59:39.454 --> 59:42.499
- You want to use the car tonight?
- What?

59:42.666 --> 59:45.585
Just drop me off at the Carpatho.

59:46.878 --> 59:51.758
- You're not going to go to the game?
- No, I'm going to go get drunk.

59:57.973 --> 01:00:04.146
