any other school?

01:06:15.391 --> 01:06:16.768
No.

01:06:17.185 --> 01:06:20.480
Pretty soon it'll be
letter-of-intent day.

01:06:20.647 --> 01:06:23.441
The last school I saw
was Walnut Heights.

01:06:23.608 --> 01:06:26.486
- How about it, Vin?
- Fuck school, man.

01:06:26.652 --> 01:06:28.821
